  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Dissynergic defecation causes solitery rectal ulcer. The biofeedback therapy improves
      dissynegy and heals soliter rectal ulcer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      dyssynergia treating ulcers caused by treatment with biofeedback
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
